---
const email = "mike@mikegomez.dev";
---

<section
  id="contact"
  class="relative py-32 sm:py-44 border-t border-iron bg-void overflow-hidden"
>
  {/* Massive bg type */}
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 -bottom-12 flex justify-center font-display uppercase text-[clamp(180px,30vw,520px)] leading-[0.85] text-flare/[0.04] select-none whitespace-nowrap"
  >
    Let&rsquo;s ship
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-14">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3 reveal">
        <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] font-mono text-flare">
          <span class="inline-block w-6 h-px bg-flare align-middle mr-2"
          ></span>
          Contact
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9 reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h2
          class="font-display uppercase leading-[0.85] text-[clamp(56px,12vw,200px)] tracking-[-0.02em]"
        >
          <span class="block">You bring</span>
          <span class="block">
            the <span class="text-flare">problem.</span>
          </span>
          <span class="block text-stroke">I bring the build.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 mt-20">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-5 md:col-start-4 reveal">
        <p class="text-paper text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Tell me what you&rsquo;re building, when it needs to launch, and
          the rough budget. I answer within one business day. If we&rsquo;re
          not a fit I&rsquo;ll tell you and point you to someone who is.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <a
            href={`mailto:${email}`}
            data-magnetic
            class="group flex items-center justify-between border-t border-iron py-5 hover:border-flare transition will-change-transform"
            data-cursor="hover"
          >
            <span>
              <span class="block font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-smoke mb-1.5">
                Email
              </span>
              <span class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-4xl uppercase tracking-[-0.01em] group-hover:text-flare transition-colors break-all">
                {email}
              </span>
            </span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-7 h-7 -rotate-45 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform flex-shrink-0 ml-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M5 12 H19 M13 6 L19 12 L13 18" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </a>

          <a
            href="#"
            data-magnetic
            class="group flex items-center justify-between border-t border-b border-iron py-5 hover:border-flare transition will-change-transform"
            data-cursor="hover"
          >
            <span>
              <span class="block font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-smoke mb-1.5">
                30 min intro call
              </span>
              <span class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl uppercase tracking-[-0.01em] group-hover:text-flare transition-colors">
                Book a slot
              </span>
            </span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-7 h-7 -rotate-45 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform flex-shrink-0 ml-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M5 12 H19 M13 6 L19 12 L13 18" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-10 font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-smoke leading-relaxed">
          Currently booking projects starting in 2&ndash;4 weeks.<br />
          Typical engagement &mdash; $4k&ndash;$25k.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
